/-- In the left-tight case, a nontrivial `π`-cycle link gives a simple direct
path between the two corresponding `(finRotate * π)` quotient vertices. -/
theorem leftTight_incidenceGraph_left_walk_of_sameCycle_isPath
    {m : ℕ} {π : Equiv.Perm (Fin (m + 1))}
    (hleft : permCycleClassCount π +
      permCycleClassCount (finRotate (m + 1) * π) = (m + 1) + 1)
