right endpoint is fixed.  The adjacent start branch is already impossible by
left-tight transversality, and the adjacent end branch is the fixed-predecessor
case. -/
theorem leftTight_contour_interval_sameCycle_frontier_of_no_internal_right_repeat
    {m : ℕ} {π : Equiv.Perm (Fin (m + 1))}
    (hleft : permCycleClassCount π +
      permCycleClassCount (finRotate (m + 1) * π) = (m + 1) + 1)
    {a c : ℕ} (ha : a ∈ Finset.range (m + 1))
    (hc : c ∈ Finset.range (m + 1)) (hac_lt : a < c)
